Name: Teagen Dix
AboutMe: I am a young, hopeful particle theorist and author who will be attending Reed College with a joint major in Philosophy-Physics. I have vocalised my support for Bernie Sanders and will be volunteering for his campaign. If you wish to contact me, my email is teagengreydix@gmail.com.
